premise_source_doc_sentence: The Minions are small , yellow , melodious henchmen who wear overalls and goggles and have one or two eyes .
The former two versions of the game were released in North America on June 26 , 2007 , then later in Europe on June 29 and Australia on July 6 , 2007 .
They have most ordinary names , with Kevin , Stuart and Bob being the names of the lead trio in Minions , and Mel being the leader of the Minions in Despicable Me 3 .
The company is best known for being the creators of the Despicable Me franchise , its spin-off/prequel Minions and the films The Secret Life of Pets and Sing .

A sequel for all three systems entitled Overlord II was announced the same year on August 13 along with a spin-off for the Nintendo Wii entitled Overlord : Dark Legend and a Nintendo DS game called Overlord : Minions .
